Package: gevplus
Title: Fitting the Generalized Extreme Value Distribution constrained to Positive Shape Parameters
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Harald", "Schellander", email = "harald.schellander@geosphere.at", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7661-287X", "Package creator and maintainer"))
Description: Extreme value analysis with a generalized extreme value distribution constrained to positive shape parameters (Moccia et al., 2021, <doi:10.1016/j.ejrh.2021.100906>). The estimation method can be selected, and return levels can be calculated, with confidence intervals. 
Maintainer: Harald Schellander <harald.schellander@geosphere.at>
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Imports: dplyr, extRemes, Lmoments
License: GPL-3
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
